// auto Suite — UI Feature Catalog (UVL Root)
// File: auto.catalog.uvl
// Tier: T2 Common
//
// Machine-readable root of the auto suite's UI feature tree.
// Imports composition node UVL files and assembles them under
// a single suite root feature.
//
// This file is imported by catalog.uvl (the platform root).
//
// Companion document: _auto_suite.md (SS6 Feature Catalog)
// ============================================================

namespace auto

imports
    // Composition nodes — authored as placeholders until leaf
    // feature specs are written. Uncomment when leaf UVL files
